2️⃣ Room

rid – IntegerField (PK)

room_no – IntegerField

room_type – CharField (AC / Non-AC / Deluxe)

price_per_day – IntegerField

is_available – BooleanField

3️⃣ Booking

bid – IntegerField (PK)

gid – ForeignKey (Guest)

rid – ForeignKey (Room)

check_in – DateField

check_out – DateField

total_days – IntegerField

status – CharField (Booked / Checked-in / Checked-out)

4️⃣ Payment

pid – IntegerField (PK)

bid – ForeignKey (Booking)

amount – IntegerField

payment_mode – CharField (Cash / UPI / Card)

